<abstract><t>This document specifies the mapping and notification of defect states between a pseudowire (PW) and the Attachment Circuits (ACs) of the end-to-end emulated service.  It standardizes the behavior of Provider Edges (PEs) with respect to PW and AC defects.  It addresses ATM, frame relay, TDM, and SONET/SDH PW services, carried over MPLS, MPLS/IP and L2TPV3/IP Packet Switched Networks (PSNs).</t></abstract>

